high_descs: Turn around and walk to the brown couch on the left.
Pick up the black credit card with blue stripes from the couch.
Turn right, take a right at the chairs and turn left to face the second brown chair.
Put the credit card on the middle of the chair.
Turn around and walk to the wooden round table with the television.
Pick up the black credit card with blue stripes from the round table.
Turn around and return to the brown chair.
Put the credit card to the right of the other card on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place two credit cards on a chair.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, hang a left, go to the couch and hang a left, go to the middle of the couch where the black pillow is.
Pick up the credit card that is on the couch.
Turn to the right, go to the chair, hang a right and go to the farthest chair.
Put the credit card down in the chair.
Hang a right, go forward, hang a right and go to the front of the table that the TV is on.
Pick up the credit card that is on the table.
Turn to the left, go forward, hang a left, go to the rightmost chair that is across from the end of the coffee table.
Put the credit card in the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards in a chair.

high_descs: Turn around for one step and turn left and walk to the end of the coffee table and take a left for three steps and then take a right to face the couch.
Pick up the credit card on the couch cushion.
Turn right for three steps, take a right for four steps and turn left to face the chair.
Put the credit card on the cushion, to the front just right of the cushion center.
Turn right for one step, turn right and walk to the end of the rug and turn right for three steps and turn left to face the TV table.
Pick up the credit card on the table.
Turn left for three steps, turn left and walk to the end of the table and turn left for one step and then turn right to face the chair.
Put the credit card on the couch cushion to the right of the credit card already there.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards on the cushion of a chair.
